Dialogue: 100,0:00:01.08,0:00:02.64,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Au trecut trei luni.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:02.64,0:00:05.23,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Trei luni și nouă zile, mai exact.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.99,0:00:09.78,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Chiar au început să crească...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.85,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Experimentul decurge foarte bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.53,Dialogue,Villagers,0,0,0,,Domnișoară cercetătoare!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.21,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.21,0:00:17.28,Dialogue,Villagers,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.38,Dialogue,Villagers,0,0,0,,Chiar cresc.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.38,0:00:23.71,Dialogue,Villagers,0,0,0,,Primarul a fost surprins.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.71,0:00:28.84,Dialogue,Villagers,0,0,0,,Deci le mărunțiți{tocați, tăiați subtirii}, le prăjiți în ulei, le puneți sare și le mâncați?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.55,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Sunt așa de bune încât nu vă veți mai putea opri din mâncat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.96,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Când va veni vremea recoltării{culegerii}, îl vom invita pe primar la o petrecere.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.58,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Voiam să lucrez câmpul alături de restul oamenilor.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.58,0:02:16.12,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Ai încercat asta o dată și a fost un dezastru total.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.12,0:02:17.90,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nu ți-ai putut stăpâni puterea.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.20,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Eram sigur că mă abțineam.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.66,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Se pare că se potrivesc{integrează} bine{perfect}.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Mă bucur să văd asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.09,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Cum a fost să ieși afară după atâta timp?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.09,0:02:33.55,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Arată bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.58,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Putem începe recoltarea{culegerea} de astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.58,0:02:36.84,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Excelent.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.38,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Alte lucruri bune de raportat?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.98,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nimic altceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.98,0:02:44.92,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Nu contează cât de neimportant ar putea părea.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.92,0:02:46.06,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nu, nimic.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.03,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Vom merge pe jos restul de drum.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.10,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Acea clădire mare de piatră e mânăstirea
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,care supraveghează călugărițele din această zonă.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.32,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Țara Lacului nu este la fel de rece precum Țara Iernii.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.89,0:03:11.84,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,E destul de departe spre nord.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.08,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Haide să ne grăbim puțin.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.66,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Biserica pune accent pe punctualitate.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.38,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.72,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Bănuiesc că toți oamenii, de la nobili la șerbi, sunt foarte devotați.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.72,0:03:24.62,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Da, nici nu-ți poți imagina.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.62,0:03:27.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,„Lumina Spiritului Luminii luminează lumea,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.14,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,aducând pace și odihnă persoanelor bune.”
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.15,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Și tu îl venerezi pe Spiritul Luminii?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.83,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Nu aș spune chiar venerat.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.99,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Când lupt, o simt aproape.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.98,0:03:45.12,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I-am auzit vocea, deci îmi e mai mult o prietenă.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.40,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Spiritul e ușor de influențat
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și nu poate refuza pe nimeni.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.42,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Mă bucur să aud asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.51,0:03:58.25,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Dacă ai fi fost un credincios devotat, mi-ar fi părut rău.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.70,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,O, nu-ți face griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.01,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Doar mi se pare că Biserica e foarte impresionantă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.69,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Toată lumea învață să scrie și să citească acolo.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și am auzit că fac și niște cercetări destul de dificile.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.15,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Nobililor cărora le pasă de astfel de lucruri
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,le pasă mai mult de Biserică decât de rege.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.86,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Sunt sigură de asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.86,0:04:23.36,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Aproape toată educația și știința oamenilor se bazează pe Biserică.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.73,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Sper să pot profita de puterea lor ca organizație.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.82,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Să mergem.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.82,0:04:30.89,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.04,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,E drăguț să vezi un oraș aglomerat din când în când.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.92,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Asta e tot?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.92,0:04:40.61,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.13,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,În acest caz, ține asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.02,Dialogue,Nun,0,0,0,,O voi chema pe Prioră imediat.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.96,Dialogue,Nun,0,0,0,,Vă rog să așteptați aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.61,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Bun, am reușit să intrăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.03,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,If negotiations fail and someone comes after us, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.70,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,No one will beat me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.17,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I wouldn't expect anyone like that to be in a convent.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.41,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,But I appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.59,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Rege al Demonilor...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.92,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Atunci, de ce fața ți s-a întristat?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.02,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Chiar s-a întâmplat asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.02,0:05:22.88,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.68,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I've seen you do it before.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.20,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.13,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.98,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nu am realizat până acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.98,0:05:34.14,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Mă deranjează de ceva vreme.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.84,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.64,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I am the Crimson Scholar, an agricultural researcher
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in one of the southern frontier villages.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Thank you for meeting with us.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.80,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Eu sunt Spadasinul Alb, gardianul ei.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.46,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm not really the type who belongs in a convent...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.88,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Spadasinul Alb?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.88,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Spadasinul Alb?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.68,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Tu ești Eroul!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.49,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Kn-Knight!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.81,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.60,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.81,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,It's been a year since I heard from you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.42,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,The four of us were traveling together to defeat the Demon King!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.69,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,And one day, you leave a message saying,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I can handle the rest myself."
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.32,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.12,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I felt bad for getting you guys involved.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.21,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.76,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.76,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Do you understand how worried I was?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.01,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.13,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.13,0:06:52.80,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,You have the nerve to show up out of nowhere with some beautiful woman?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.64,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.68,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Wha? Well, she's...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.49,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.68,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,She's what?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.41,0:07:05.36,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Ah, I can explain that.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.28,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And thus, he managed to wound the Demon King.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when so many demons came to retaliate, he had to retreat.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.87,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Then I met him by chance and offered to take care of him
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until he could recover from his injuries.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:19.33,0:07:23.59,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,As thanks, he's now serving as my bodyguard.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.21,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.63,0:07:30.12,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for reacting as I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.15,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's fine, so long as you understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.20,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.97,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,How did you become a prioress?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.98,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,It was after I reported that you had gone to the Demon King's castle alone...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.85,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,A month later, I received a letter.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.57,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,It said the Hero had sacrificed himself to wound the Demon King.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.91,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,So they sent all of his companions a reward.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.95,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,But I didn't want it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.75,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Getting rich off your death...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.80,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,So I returned to this convent, where I had been knighted,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I tried to help everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.55,0:08:08.09,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.59,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,You really are manly, Knight.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.61,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Manly?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.43,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,So don't hide your personality.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.10,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.82,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,t-trying to hide anything...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.60,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Don't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.04,0:08:24.85,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.19,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I finally got good at acting feminine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.08,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Well? Where are the other two?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.16,0:08:37.66,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,The old pervert said he'd go and work for an intelligence group in one of the southern countries.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.09,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.40,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,He took the money.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.46,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.12,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Sounds like he's moving up.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.04,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Hero...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.88,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,And what about Mage?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.34,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,She took the money, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.26,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,She doesn't look it, but she's quite stingy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.95,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Well, she's a fun girl at least.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.23,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,She left on her own.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.47,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,She went to the Demon World to look for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.55,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,She did?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.12,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,You did try to stop her?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.59,0:09:08.87,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,But the next morning, all her things were gone.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.87,0:09:09.75,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.78,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Don't let it get you down.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.87,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,This was all my fault to begin with.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.28,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,And you know how she is.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.12,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,She won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.41,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Hero...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.22,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm here for the Scholar today.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.22,0:09:31.92,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I've come to petition your convent for aid.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.38,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,First, I'd like to show you this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.67,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.43,0:09:39.22,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,A plant, known as a potato, that grows underground.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.48,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It appears the food I asked for is here.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.82,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,The food?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.57,Dialogue,Nun,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.87,Dialogue,Nun,0,0,0,,I prepared it just as you requested.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.82,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.44,0:10:00.70,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.26,0:10:02.12,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.40,0:10:03.79,Dialogue,K,0,0,14,,Excuse me, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.67,Dialogue,Y,0,0,14,,You see?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.09,Dialogue,K,0,0,14,,Yes, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.59,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's very nutritious,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.59,0:10:17.09,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,and because it grows underground, it's difficult for birds to reach.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.84,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Also, it will grow in poor soil or colder climates,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.18,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,as well as in hard ground.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.95,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.51,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Of course, it isn't perfect.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.94,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,First, it's poisonous.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.18,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.18,0:10:33.45,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's only toxic after exposure to sunlight, when it's begun to bud.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.25,0:10:37.44,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If you take care in harvesting and storing it, it's perfectly safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.41,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,In a cold place, you can store it for nearly a year.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.96,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,A year?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.96,0:10:46.84,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Under the right conditions, it can be harvested three times a year.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.37,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,As a result, the harvest for a given area
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,yields three times more than wheat.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.39,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.01,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I've already experimented with it at Winter's Pass Village.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.01,0:11:02.43,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,If that's true, we'll be able to save many starving people.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.19,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.19,0:11:07.96,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,If you're seeking our financial support...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.23,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I regret to inform you that...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.33,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,No, I'd be happy if you could offer it,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.82,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,but that is not my immediate objective.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.53,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Then what would you have of us?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.73,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I want you to establish a convent in Winter's Pass Village.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.73,0:11:25.55,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And then, I'd like you to teach the villagers new,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,more effective agricultural methods.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.37,0:11:31.21,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,That falls perfectly within our convent's mission.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:31.21,0:11:35.04,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And then, I would like you to build convents in surrounding areas,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to further spread knowledge of this new method.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.26,0:11:41.18,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,How does this benefit you, Scholar?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.01,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If we move forward,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.06,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,we can see what's on the other side of the hill.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.80,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,A future without war,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.56,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,a world without starvation.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.48,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If potato planting becomes common,{once the potato becomes mass produced, the federation is over!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the food situation improves,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.23,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I'm sure we will get closer.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.56,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I wish to see the other side of the hill.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.28,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.55,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.55,0:12:15.63,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,The convent will provide all it can to assist you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.65,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.17,0:12:22.34,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,{\move(640,690,1280,690,3988,4155)}Then I shall go to Winter's Pass Village personally.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.30,0:12:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(130,690)}You will?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.34,0:12:22.38,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,690)}You will?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.38,0:12:22.42,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,{\pos(565,690)}You will?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.38,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,{\move(640,690,0,690,739,989)}You will?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.93,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,{\move(1020,690,640,690,0,111)}Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.93,0:12:25.09,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,{\move(640,690,1280,690)}Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.98,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,{\move(100,690,640,690,0,72)}No...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.20,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.20,0:12:31.77,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Haven't I always been a nihilistic, dangerous hero?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.10,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,So being close to me could endanger you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.85,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,I'm used to that!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.22,0:12:39.23,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Or is there another reason you'd prefer I didn't go?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.36,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,No, well...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,What troubles you?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.26,0:12:48.20,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You're being quite rude to the head of the convent, who has offered us aid.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.52,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Nothing would make me happier.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.58,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I would welcome you.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.12,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,You seem unconcerned.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.49,0:12:59.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I always have the greatest respect for those with whom I form a contract.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.35,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.35,0:13:05.97,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Then I shall answer in kind, in accordance with the laws of chivalry.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.69,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,First you return after I'd already given up on seeing you again.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.70,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,And then, there's this wonderful food the Scholar brought us.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.37,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,It must be the Light Spirit's guidance.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.66,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,No, this was accomplished purely by human hands.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.64,0:13:36.96,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The product of hard work done by those with souls.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.21,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm glad your secret weapon worked.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.46,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.16,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,But I wasn't expecting to see your ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.33,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Don't call her that!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.07,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Is she not?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.07,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.51,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,She and I...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.31,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,We aren't like that...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll stop bringing it up.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.32,0:13:56.81,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.02,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,Lately, you've been locked in your room all the time.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.02,0:14:00.86,Dialogue,K,0,0,0,,What have you been doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.86,0:14:05.21,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If we stay in one place and rely solely on the bounty of the land,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.86,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,we'll run into problems before long.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.88,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,You mean the soil will deplete?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.85,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.41,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And so we must make an offering to the land.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.36,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Burnt crops, the bodies of animals...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.08,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Manure and leftover food.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.45,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Best of all would be fish from the southern ice seas.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.34,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'll buy some and bring them back...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.17,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,with my teleportation magic!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.11,0:14:28.84,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,We'd need 30,000 a year for Winter's Pass Village alone.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.39,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe not.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.68,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And the Ice General dwells in the southern ice seas.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I've fought him many times.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.15,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,He's huge and was unstoppable with a harpoon.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.15,0:14:45.15,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,He's one of the most warmongering demons, as well as one of the strongest.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.65,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Clashing with him would complicate things.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.04,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,But the bigger problem is the Alliance.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.66,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Alliance?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.09,0:14:57.37,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Their full name is the Economic Alliance of Free Merchants and Southern Independent Cities.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.09,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,So it's a merchant group, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.42,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.25,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,They're based primarily here, in the south,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but their reach extends across the entire continent.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.79,0:15:11.22,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,My estimates suggest their total capital is astronomical.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.48,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,In the south alone,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.48,0:15:16.35,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,the Alliance is involved in 60 percent of the wheat trade.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.61,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If they desired it, they're powerful enough to dethrone a king.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.30,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,What kind of monsters are they?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.20,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, they're monsters.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And human life rests on these monsters' backs.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.85,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,So that was the Alliance, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.56,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,They asked me to give some speeches for them.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.65,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,"Up and at 'em!"
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.66,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,That kind of thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.95,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's propaganda.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,They paid you several million in gold pieces, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.33,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,More like fifteen!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Only fifteen?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.01,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,These girls in flashy dresses came out and said,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"We love you, Hero!"
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.05,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Girls in flashy dresses?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.68,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,And the guy from the Alliance told me,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When you return, we'll throw a victory parade!"
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.20,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,And he gave me a nudge me and said, "You sure are popular."
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.36,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,I'm a failure as a hero...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.17,0:16:09.37,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I guess you require a harsh lesson.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.20,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The Alliance has no will of its own.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.74,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Their sole interest is self-protection and expansion.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.58,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,That's what makes them worth using.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.46,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,But that's not what's important.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.96,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,What have I been doing in my room these last two months?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.59,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.76,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.72,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,A compass.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.34,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,I've never seen one like it before.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.32,0:16:37.84,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,These two circles keep it level, no matter the conditions.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.70,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,It doesn't use any kind of special device.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.60,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.78,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,This is splendid!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.78,0:16:48.98,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,You could be one of the leaders. Maybe even join the Council of Ten!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.90,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,Yes, this will change the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,Yeah! It will.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.37,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,It will bring the Alliance great wealth.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,But there's a problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.37,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.18,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.18,0:17:10.30,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,Someone else invented this and gave it to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.09,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,We must consider what they're after.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.70,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.95,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,Do you know who it is?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.97,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,They fancy themselves "the Crimson Scholar."
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.97,0:17:23.64,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,They live in Winter's Pass, an isolated village in the Southern Nations.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.30,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,It appears to be a normal frontier village,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,producing nothing of particular account.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.98,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.44,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.39,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,The Elder of Winter's Pass Village
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.39,0:17:38.29,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,is in negotiations with the Lakeside Convent of the Lake Country.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.24,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you have that information.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.24,0:17:44.52,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,Someone wondered why they would approach the convent of such a distant land,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and so they reported to us.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,Indeed, it is suspicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.38,0:17:51.25,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,If they're involved, this could be problematic.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.21,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.55,0:17:54.01,Dialogue,OM,0,0,0,,We must ensure that
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,only the Alliance benefits from this compass.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.72,0:18:04.06,Dialogue,A,0,0,0,,We'll just have to pray it hasn't been sold to anyone other than us.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.23,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.92,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,I am a simple merchant.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.36,Dialogue,YM,0,0,0,,I have no wish to be an assassin.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.48,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,You're expecting a visitor?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.65,Dialogue,Mb,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.78,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,Then take this rabbit to the Scholar.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.78,0:18:22.64,Dialogue,Mb,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.32,Dialogue,Ms,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.37,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,And here's some watercress from the swamp.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.77,Dialogue,Ms,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hooray!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.77,Dialogue,Mb,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.84,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.84,0:18:32.46,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, the village is much brighter.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.21,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,You are both very beautiful.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.80,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,They were born to a different life than ours.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.24,Dialogue,Villager,0,0,0,,Everyone admires you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.19,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You're fully armored at this hour?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.90,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Demon King!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.88,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You can't stop worrying about her, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.26,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.91,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Did you think I would stop you?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.31,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,You're okay with this?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.57,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,If Mage is another girlfriend of yours, maybe not.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.09,0:19:07.75,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.01,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.25,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.36,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.79,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It isn't cursed in any way.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.56,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,The Demon World is starting to get lax in my absence.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.28,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I'd like you to go and take care of the rowdier ones.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.28,0:19:33.11,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.14,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I have a list, with letters of introduction,
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the leaders I think you can trust.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.96,0:19:41.09,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You'll need their help if you're looking for someone.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.20,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You should be grateful for my kindness.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.64,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.10,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.62,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,That's it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.72,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,That's, well... In the Human World...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.54,0:19:57.31,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,There's a special ritual men and women who are close perform when parting!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.76,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Do you refuse because of my useless flesh?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.15,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,N-No, well...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.65,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Maybe we do need to be closer physically...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.24,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.93,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Well, the Head Maid said...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.12,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'm overstepping myself,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:12.12,0:20:16.82,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,but you two haven't even held hands for almost two months, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.72,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,H-How did you know our secret?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.40,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,I could tell by observing.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.95,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,He is a virgin,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:22.95,0:20:25.82,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,so you must go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.49,0:20:33.50,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,You've spent the past two months locked in your room, ignoring the Hero.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,I knew it,0,0,0,,Your useless flesh coefficient is increasing.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.44,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.92,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Your clothes aren't revealing enough, and you aren't cute enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.87,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,If you're stingy with physical contact, what's left?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.26,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.80,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.93,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,In war, the most important thing is quantity.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.93,0:20:53.78,Dialogue,Ma,0,0,0,,Surround and overwhelm a man's reason,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you don't even need strategy!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.66,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Technically, she's right, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.71,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Is it not okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.61,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Ah! It's e-embarrassing!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.61,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,We should do it when we aren't so busy.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.78,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Six months!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.15,0:21:10.79,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,It's tearing me up that I should have a clear advantage,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after spending all this time with you in the snow...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.96,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,And six months have passed, with no changes at all!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:17.96,0:21:21.50,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,Additionally, once the convent is complete, your first girlfriend will arrive,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.67,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,and you're leaving to search for your second girlfriend!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.68,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,How could it not bother me?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.51,0:21:33.04,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.86,0:21:47.20,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Why do you look so mad?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.49,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,That was on the forehead.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.33,Dialogue,Y,0,0,0,,We'll do the rest when I get back.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.74,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You'd better promise, Hero!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.38,Dialogue,M,0,0,0,,You'd better...
